This paper is about visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. The use of deep reinforcement learning and decision-net for selecting the optimal correlation filter model suggests that this paper belongs to the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and multimedia (cs.MM).
